    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a strong finish, though you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all electronics functioning as intended and only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable and attractive option for its next owner.",
