    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant repairs to be roadworthy again. The engine currently struggles to stay running, and there are noticeable leaks throughout the undercarriage. The body shows heavy rust in several areas, and the interior upholstery is badly torn and stained. This car is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a parts donor.",
