    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, featuring a flawless factory finish with no chips or imperfections. The interior retains its original scent, with supple leather and high-gloss trim that show zero signs of wear. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been maintained exclusively at authorized centers with a complete, documented service history. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning enthusiast to own a vehicle that has been pampered in a climate-controlled garage and never driven in inclement weather. The sale includes all original keys, owner's manuals, and a fitted custom car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
